00:30:51.269 --> 00:30:53.069
so I'll do better-paying day labour for a while.

00:30:53.239 --> 00:30:56.809
Why? Is something wrong? Is it about your father-in-law?

00:30:57.079 --> 00:30:59.579
Why bring up my father-in-law out of the blue?

00:30:59.949 --> 00:31:01.649
No, that's not it. It's just...

00:31:02.049 --> 00:31:05.619
The practical test is in a few days, and if you pass,

00:31:05.749 --> 00:31:08.389
you're going to start looking for an electrician job, right?

