This might not be the time to relax and just earn enough to get by.

00:31:16.359 --> 00:31:19.569
- I have to go. - Hey, stay for a drink. It's on me.

00:31:19.629 --> 00:31:21.069
You said nothing was wrong at home.

00:31:21.139 --> 00:31:25.069
I can't drink or goof off. Take it easy.

00:31:27.579 --> 00:31:29.209
Something's definitely up with Lee Sang Cheol.

