I thought he didn't come home last night.

00:32:12.419 --> 00:32:14.589
Look, just go downstairs first. We can talk downstairs.

00:32:14.659 --> 00:32:15.989
- Come on, let's go. - What? Why?

00:32:16.059 --> 00:32:18.289
- Downstairs, come on. - What is going on?

00:32:25.099 --> 00:32:29.369
You're saying he's been holed up in his room since last night?

00:32:29.569 --> 00:32:32.139
