If he snuck in quietly last night, something's seriously wrong with it.

00:32:37.309 --> 00:32:39.909
So what if there is a problem, and so what if there isn't?

00:32:40.579 --> 00:32:43.279
Gosh, will you just tell Ji Hyuk to come down?

00:32:43.349 --> 00:32:45.319
Mother, just pretend you don't know anything.

