00:32:53.129 --> 00:32:54.129
Ji Wan, you too.

00:32:56.429 --> 00:32:59.929
Try to stay out of his way today, if you can.

00:33:00.569 --> 00:33:02.539
- Mother, just go to your room. - All right, I'm going.

00:33:02.869 --> 00:33:06.569
So that means Ji Hyuk hasn't eaten anything all day.

00:33:06.639 --> 00:33:09.439
He'll come down and eat on his own if he's hungry.

