I couldn't secure the funds for the acquisition.

00:34:33.889 --> 00:34:35.699
What would you do if you were in my shoes, Dad?

00:34:36.259 --> 00:34:38.299
If it were me, I'd go see the chairman himself.

00:34:38.799 --> 00:34:39.799
What?

00:34:40.129 --> 00:34:42.139
You have to crawl over that mountain if that's what it takes.

00:34:42.439 --> 00:34:43.699
That's the only way to have no regrets.

00:34:45.639 --> 00:34:50.009
Dad, you don't understand business, but it all comes down to money.

00:34:51.509 --> 00:34:54.779
There are two other companies with their full funds ready.

00:34:54.919 --> 00:34:56.019
And there could be more for all I know.

