The meaning of that money changes depending on the person holding it.

00:35:19.809 --> 00:35:20.809
See?

00:35:21.909 --> 00:35:23.909
What have you got to lose?

00:35:24.609 --> 00:35:26.149
For someone who acts like such a know-it-all.

00:35:26.879 --> 00:35:28.879
You can't live with regrets, can you?

00:35:29.619 --> 00:35:33.189
You went all the way to the altar. So you have no regrets, right?

00:35:33.319 --> 00:35:36.859
If you hadn't, you'd spend your life wondering what if and being bitter.

00:35:37.429 --> 00:35:40.429
Gosh. What does that have to do with anything?

00:35:41.599 --> 00:35:43.459
I bought that hotteok.

00:35:45.569 --> 00:35:47.739
Fine, how much were they? What? How much do I owe you?

