Everyone's been looking to me for answers.

00:43:03.569 --> 00:43:04.569
Mr. Lee?

00:43:06.169 --> 00:43:08.609
Carry on with your work. I haven't...

00:43:09.139 --> 00:43:10.709
given up on AP.

