My mind's a bit of a mess today,

00:43:13.649 --> 00:43:16.649
so I need everyone to please focus on their assigned tasks.

00:43:26.489 --> 00:43:27.489
Did you sleep well?

00:43:30.559 --> 00:43:31.699
See you later.

