Mr. Ha, this is Lee Ji Hyuk.

00:45:07.259 --> 00:45:09.729
Mr. Lee. Are you feeling calmer now?

00:45:10.799 --> 00:45:13.469
Moment M and A is still my advisor, correct?

00:45:13.929 --> 00:45:14.939
Because I'm...

00:45:16.099 --> 00:45:17.269
going to see this through to the end.

00:45:17.899 --> 00:45:19.209
What do you mean by that?

00:45:21.739 --> 00:45:23.009
Chairman Kim Dong Su...

00:45:23.809 --> 00:45:25.149
I'm going to meet him in person.

